==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ML.}} {{term|lang=la|secretarius||one entrusted with secrets}} < {{etyl|la}} {{term|lang=la|secretus||private, secret}}, past participle of {{term|lang=la|secernere||to separate, set apart}} < {{term|lang=la|se-||apart}} + {{term|lang=la|cernere||to separate}}.

